Both the European Institute for Climate and Energy (EIKE) and Die kalte Sonne sites have announced that renown scientist Murry Salby¬†will be speaking on climate in Hamburg.

Salby at a presentation in Sydney. Source here.
Professor Salby of the Macquarie University in Sydney has been invited by the Helmut Schmidt University and is scheduled to speak at 11 a.m. on April 18th. The precise location: Helmut-Schmidt-Universit√§t; Universit√§t der Bundeswehr Hamburg; Fakult√§t f√ºr Elektrotechnik, Mensa Thomas Ellwein Saal.


